      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DEEP THINKER (2) turned in a fair 4th placed finish last time at Horsham over 485m (27.61). Was a winner at his only start from this draw. Worth another chance. LAURA MAY (3) turned in a better effort at Shepparton last start, finishing third behind Aussie Raven (25.72) in a Rank Limit - Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Yet to score from this box but has never missed the frame in three starts. Expecting another good run. PAW JERRY (1) had been racing in honest fashion recording two placings in a row before finishing fifth (31.08) at The Meadows latest. Can measure up this time. TIME PERPETUATED (5) scored last time and can measure up again.",
